{"tid":991914,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[ Apple ]今年蘋果應該點樣做返好？","createTime":"2019-01-22T17:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T13:40:42.000Z","uid":140303,"like":6,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c713891f0a859b22e1aa216b0fb62d459b5caa8a","tid":991914,"uid":140303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T17:37:19.000Z","msg":"個人意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\niPhone: <br />\n今年條Line 唔好再出XR 因為定價好尷尬剩係出XI XI  Max就好足夠<br />\n今年最好就XI同XI Max 調低個價錢 10%都好<br />\n<br />\n之後出SE 2 用iPhone 6s 個款 用A10粒U 賣3000-4000 踢走iPhone 7 <br />\n<br />\niPad:<br />\n新iPad Mini &amp; iPad 2019 就用A11 最好支援新pencil <br />\nMini 用翻舊Mini 個form factor 就得 價錢就跟翻2018 iPad 我都覺得幾好 mini 就平佢200至300都幾好<br />\n<br />\niPod:<br />\n再玩大啲就出翻iPod touch不過要有3.5mm 用A9 都得 再加個hifi dac 落去 再update 埋apple music 可以支援FLAC File <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賣3500都幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMac:<br />\n電腦就最好出Modular Mac 因為好多人都等緊<br />\n<br />\nMacBook: <br />\nMacBook 就cut 咗MacBook 佢 淨係保留MacBook Air同埋MacBook Pro 因為佢The MacBook 仲輕過air 令人混淆<br />\n<br />\n如果可以嘅話 最好MacBook Pro都轉用face ID <br />\n<br />\n因為其實MacBook 用face ID係好方便嘅一件事 <br />\n<br />\n大家有咩提議或者有咩想蘋果今年會出？"},{"pid":"f7ac0969bf90c9615b191609fba68bd24a37e9e0","tid":991914,"uid":140303,"like":1,"dislike":36,"score":-35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T17:44:11.000Z","msg":"個人覺得iPhone今年嘅價位:(理想)<br />\n<br />\n8199 iPhone XI <br />\n8899 iPhone XI Max<br />\n<br />\n7399 iPhone XS<br />\n8099 iPhone XS Max <br />\n5799 iPhone XR <br />\n<br />\n4899 iPhone 8 Plus<br />\n4299 iPhone 8<br />\n<br />\n3499 iPhone SE 2"},{"pid":"0ed4776a6a3301c4aa2506b4d577167f36e80af8","tid":991914,"uid":140303,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T17:45:26.000Z","msg":"咁快已經有兩個負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c279526546bead94dc8667a