有得諗<br />\n配埋itunes真係會方便<br />\n不過如果連部iphone都支援就更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢應該唔會再放咁多心思去搞獨特性<br />\n目前幾代都係更新硬件就算<br />\n已準備失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：用緊sp1000"},{"pid":"bd43400060b9a54deda5846468e6058b9b852c23","tid":991914,"uid":79023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T18:20:04.000Z","msg":"出市場無既新product<br />\n咁先創新"},{"pid":"8a5b1a22b907bcb55d98684198016ce5787d0f27","tid":991914,"uid":9616,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T18:58:27.000Z","msg":"#1 繼續iOS12 fix好左嘅野再build up上去，咪再亂咁搞出好似iOS11嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n#2 停止機海，因為真係唔work 5C試左次，XR又黎。<br />\n<br />\n#3 成皮野買你部電話，你送嘅accessory 5W charger，然後同人講你又support fast charge， USB-C to lightning 同新brick都冇跟機，麻煩跟番好你promote果d新少少嘅配件。<br />\n<br />\n#4 mac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個keyboard 真係各花入各眼，手感唔講。但最近2018 MBA又俾人話入塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉design都由2016搞起，整到第3代新機，都仲係會咁，同部機最基本互動嘅野都會穿崩，仲講乜野macOS同iOS整合度高？<br />\n<br />\n#5 iPad 9.7 10.5 11 每一年變一次size，app未support好又改resolution，總會慢慢變到iPad app scale support得唔好。 決定左screen size/ resolution/ scale 就用到尾啦?<br />\n<br />\n#6 吸引人買野，係因為有新功能，大提升。定到咁貴，功能俾上代係好左少少，d人梗係揀換電，用番本來部野等你出新啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#7 整好Apple Watch 同有一部真。入門iPhone（更新SE？)，成個bundle咁sell，先會俾其他本來非ios用家體驗到成日sell嘅eco system。本來曾經有iPod touch慢慢引人買iPhone，依家價錢離地到本身用緊都唔想升，又冇新人加入，最後只會食曬老本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579cdb3721b320fa65c197f18c52157f18adc3ef","tid":991914,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:05:21.000Z","msg":"iPhone<br />\n3.5<br />\n無M<br />\n無凸<br />\n<br />\n+<br />\n<br />\nMac<br />\n3.5<br />\n普通usb<br />\nsd卡槽<br />\n<br />\n=大賣"},{"pid":"4284ed47f90e5f13f44487eef54d5459c5546c72","tid":991914,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfbc8fa681823183ec0efde11f5ade84993e632b","tid":991914,"uid":137647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T18:10:05.000Z","msg":"Ipod如果支援hi res其實有得諗<br />\n配埋itunes真係會方便<br />\n不過如果連部iphone都支援就更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢應該唔會再放咁多心思去搞獨特性<br />\n目前幾代都係更新硬件就算<br />\n已準備失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：用緊sp1000"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:09:47.000Z","msg":"iPod唔玩hifi果邊根本冇意義出落去"},{"pid":"92735f76d1a0558b8ad6ca1e2de57491cb635fa7","tid":991914,"uid":1130,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:12:59.000Z","msg":"XR唔係失敗 亦唔係5C <br />\n5C收皮係因為A6+膠 仲要唔平5S好多<br />\n<br />\n今年失敗係個戇鳩女人亂定價 又cut呢樣嗰樣 <br />\n成皮嘢仲跟緊5W charger"},{"pid":"24ef1421918cf6ffe40be48d0999848b6e9fd732","tid":991914,"uid":126508,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:25:55.000Z","msg":"今年班人多左4000蚊 香港版應該全線加多3500-4000蚊 唔係點賺到盡？"},{"pid":"f57985b2721f542b14a801e4deb1f0d88e38e61f","tid":991914,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T19:55:12.000Z","msg":"好心 cut 左 7,7p,8,8p,xr<br />\n出一部iphone se左右size 既iphone se2 比窮撚用,最緊要有3.5mm, A10, 膠殼,最好做到fullscreen, 賣4699 128gb<br />\n<br />\n其他人焗佢買 xi xi max<br />\nxi xi max 最低轉做 128gb<br />\n賣7288 &amp; 8288 <br />\n<br />\n撚下班ipad mini撚, 唔出ipad mini 5<br />\n出 ipad pro 8.5 行A12x, 焗班想換機既友仔上pro<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上左pro 就一世都返唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"86ee6e036a1080da7db88b20ee92eac97656b29c","tid":991914,"uid":4285,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T23:59:22.000Z","msg":"俾d 誠意隨機送翻個快差先啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"2187a34a8fcbfcc98f063c220c880ea0ff9a091a","tid":991914,"uid":140303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"11decd2da13fb2034